{
  "video_id": "wPFA8n7goio",
  "title": "3 ways the brain creates meaning | Tom Wujec",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 16160.0,
      "text": "Last year at TED we aimed to try to clarify"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16160.0,
      "end_time": 18160.0,
      "text": "the overwhelming complexity"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18160.0,
      "end_time": 21160.0,
      "text": "and richness that we experience at the conference"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21160.0,
      "end_time": 23160.0,
      "text": "in a project called Big Viz."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23160.0,
      "end_time": 26160.0,
      "text": "And the Big Viz is a collection of 650 sketches"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26160.0,
      "end_time": 28160.0,
      "text": "that were made by two visual artists."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28160.0,
      "end_time": 30160.0,
      "text": "David Sibbet from The Grove,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30160.0,
      "end_time": 32159.0,
      "text": "and Kevin Richards, from Autodesk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32159.0,
      "end_time": 35160.0,
      "text": "made 650 sketches that strive to capture"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35160.0,
      "end_time": 39160.0,
      "text": "the essence of each presenter&#39;s ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39160.0,
      "end_time": 41160.0,
      "text": "And the consensus was: it really worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41160.0,
      "end_time": 45160.0,
      "text": "These sketches brought to life the key ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45160.0,
      "end_time": 47160.0,
      "text": "the portraits, the magic moments"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47160.0,
      "end_time": 49160.0,
      "text": "that we all experienced last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49160.0,
      "end_time": 52160.0,
      "text": "This year we were thinking, \"Why does it work?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52160.0,
      "end_time": 54160.0,
      "text": "What is it about animation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54160.0,
      "end_time": 57160.0,
      "text": "graphics, illustrations, that create meaning?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57160.0,
      "end_time": 60160.0,
      "text": "And this is an important question to ask and answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60160.0,
      "end_time": 63160.0,
      "text": "because the more we understand how the brain creates meaning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63160.0,
      "end_time": 65160.0,
      "text": "the better we can communicate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65160.0,
      "end_time": 68160.0,
      "text": "and, I also think, the better we can think and collaborate together."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68160.0,
      "end_time": 70160.0,
      "text": "So this year we&#39;re going to visualize how"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70160.0,
      "end_time": 72160.0,
      "text": "the brain visualizes."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72160.0,
      "end_time": 74160.0,
      "text": "Cognitive psychologists now tell us that the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74160.0,
      "end_time": 77160.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t actually see the world as it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77160.0,
      "end_time": 80160.0,
      "text": "but instead, creates a series of mental models"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80160.0,
      "end_time": 82160.0,
      "text": "through a collection of \"Ah-ha moments,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82160.0,
      "end_time": 84160.0,
      "text": "or moments of discovery, through various processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84160.0,
      "end_time": 87160.0,
      "text": "The processing, of course, begins with the eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87160.0,
      "end_time": 90160.0,
      "text": "Light enters, hits the back of the retina, and is circulated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90160.0,
      "end_time": 93160.0,
      "text": "most of which is streamed to the very back of the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93160.0,
      "end_time": 95160.0,
      "text": "at the primary visual cortex."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95160.0,
      "end_time": 98160.0,
      "text": "And primary visual cortex sees just simple geometry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98160.0,
      "end_time": 100160.0,
      "text": "just the simplest of shapes."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100160.0,
      "end_time": 103160.0,
      "text": "But it also acts like a kind of relay station"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 103160.0,
      "end_time": 105160.0,
      "text": "that re-radiates and redirects information"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105160.0,
      "end_time": 108160.0,
      "text": "to many other parts of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108160.0,
      "end_time": 111160.0,
      "text": "As many as 30 other parts that selectively make more sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111160.0,
      "end_time": 114160.0,
      "text": "create more meaning through the kind of \"Ah-ha\" experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114160.0,
      "end_time": 116160.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re only going to talk about three of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116160.0,
      "end_time": 119160.0,
      "text": "So the first one is called the ventral stream."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119160.0,
      "end_time": 121160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s on this side of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121160.0,
      "end_time": 125160.0,
      "text": "And this is the part of the brain that will recognize what something is."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125160.0,
      "end_time": 127160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the \"what\" detector."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127160.0,
      "end_time": 131160.0,
      "text": "Look at a hand. Look at a remote control. Chair. Book."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 131160.0,
      "end_time": 134160.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s the part of the brain that is activated"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 134160.0,
      "end_time": 136160.0,
      "text": "when you give a word to something."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136160.0,
      "end_time": 139160.0,
      "text": "A second part of the brain is called the dorsal stream."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139160.0,
      "end_time": 142160.0,
      "text": "And what it does is locates the object"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 142160.0,
      "end_time": 145160.0,
      "text": "in physical body space."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 145160.0,
      "end_time": 147160.0,
      "text": "So if you look around the stage here"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 147160.0,
      "end_time": 150160.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll create a kind of mental map of the stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 150160.0,
      "end_time": 153160.0,
      "text": "And if you closed your eyes you&#39;d be able to mentally navigate it."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153160.0,
      "end_time": 156160.0,
      "text": "You&#39;d be activating the dorsal stream if you did that."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156160.0,
      "end_time": 158160.0,
      "text": "The third part that I&#39;d like to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 158160.0,
      "end_time": 160160.0,
      "text": "is the limbic system."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 160160.0,
      "end_time": 163160.0,
      "text": "And this is deep inside of the brain. It&#39;s very old, evolutionarily."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 163160.0,
      "end_time": 165160.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s the part that feels."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 165160.0,
      "end_time": 167160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the kind of gut center, where you see an image"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 167160.0,
      "end_time": 169160.0,
      "text": "and you go, \"Oh! I have a strong"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 169160.0,
      "end_time": 173160.0,
      "text": "or emotional reaction to whatever I&#39;m seeing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 173160.0,
      "end_time": 176160.0,
      "text": "So the combination of these processing centers"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 176160.0,
      "end_time": 180160.0,
      "text": "help us make meaning in very different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 180160.0,
      "end_time": 183160.0,
      "text": "So what can we learn about this? How can we apply this insight?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 183160.0,
      "end_time": 185160.0,
      "text": "Well, again, the schematic view"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 185160.0,
      "end_time": 188160.0,
      "text": "is that the eye visually interrogates what we look at."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 188160.0,
      "end_time": 191160.0,
      "text": "The brain processes this in parallel, the figments of information"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 191160.0,
      "end_time": 193160.0,
      "text": "asking a whole bunch of questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 193160.0,
      "end_time": 195160.0,
      "text": "to create a unified mental model."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 195160.0,
      "end_time": 198160.0,
      "text": "So, for example, when you look at this image"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 198160.0,
      "end_time": 201160.0,
      "text": "a good graphic invites the eye to dart around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 201160.0,
      "end_time": 203160.0,
      "text": "to selectively create a visual logic."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 203160.0,
      "end_time": 208160.0,
      "text": "So the act of engaging, and looking at the image creates the meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 208160.0,
      "end_time": 210160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the selective logic."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 210160.0,
      "end_time": 213160.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;ve augmented this and spatialized this information."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 213160.0,
      "end_time": 216160.0,
      "text": "Many of you may remember the magic wall that we built"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 216160.0,
      "end_time": 218160.0,
      "text": "in conjunction with Perceptive Pixel"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 218160.0,
      "end_time": 221160.0,
      "text": "where we quite literally create an infinite wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 221160.0,
      "end_time": 223160.0,
      "text": "And so we can compare and contrast the big ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 223160.0,
      "end_time": 226160.0,
      "text": "So the act of engaging and creating interactive imagery"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 226160.0,
      "end_time": 228160.0,
      "text": "enriches meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 228160.0,
      "end_time": 231160.0,
      "text": "It activates a different part of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 231160.0,
      "end_time": 233160.0,
      "text": "And then the limbic system"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 233160.0,
      "end_time": 236160.0,
      "text": "is activated when we see motion, when we see color,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 236160.0,
      "end_time": 239160.0,
      "text": "and there are primary shapes and pattern detectors"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 239160.0,
      "end_time": 241160.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;ve heard about before."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 241160.0,
      "end_time": 243160.0,
      "text": "So the point of this is what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 243160.0,
      "end_time": 246160.0,
      "text": "We make meaning by seeing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 246160.0,
      "end_time": 248160.0,
      "text": "by an act of visual interrogation."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 248160.0,
      "end_time": 250160.0,
      "text": "The lessons for us are three-fold."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 250160.0,
      "end_time": 254160.0,
      "text": "First, use images to clarify what we&#39;re trying to communicate."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 254160.0,
      "end_time": 257159.0,
      "text": "Secondly make those images interactive"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 257160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259160.00000000003,
      "text": "so that we engage much more fully."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 259160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "text": "And the third is to augment memory"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263160.0,
      "text": "by creating a visual persistence."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 263160.0,
      "end_time": 266160.0,
      "text": "These are techniques that can be used to be --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 266160.0,
      "end_time": 270160.0,
      "text": "that can be applied in a wide range of problem solving."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 270160.0,
      "end_time": 272160.0,
      "text": "So the low-tech version looks like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 272160.0,
      "end_time": 274160.0,
      "text": "And, by the way, this is the way in which"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 274160.0,
      "end_time": 276160.0,
      "text": "we develop and formulate"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 276160.0,
      "end_time": 278160.0,
      "text": "strategy within Autodesk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 278160.0,
      "end_time": 281160.0,
      "text": "in some of our organizations and some of our divisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 281160.0,
      "end_time": 283160.0,
      "text": "What we literally do is have the teams"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 283160.0,
      "end_time": 286160.0,
      "text": "draw out the entire strategic plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 286160.0,
      "end_time": 288160.0,
      "text": "on one giant wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 288160.0,
      "end_time": 292160.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s very powerful because everyone gets to see everything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 292160.0,
      "end_time": 294160.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s always a room, always a place"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 294160.0,
      "end_time": 297160.0,
      "text": "to be able to make sense of all of the components"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 297160.0,
      "end_time": 299160.0,
      "text": "in the strategic plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 299160.0,
      "end_time": 302160.0,
      "text": "This is a time-lapse view of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 302160.0,
      "end_time": 304160.0,
      "text": "You can ask the question, \"Who&#39;s the boss?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 304160.0,
      "end_time": 312160.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll be able to figure that out. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 312160.0,
      "end_time": 315160.0,
      "text": "So the act of collectively and collaboratively"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 315160.0,
      "end_time": 317160.0,
      "text": "building the image"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 317160.0,
      "end_time": 320160.0,
      "text": "transforms the collaboration."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 320160.0,
      "end_time": 322160.0,
      "text": "No Powerpoint is used in two days."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 322160.0,
      "end_time": 324160.0,
      "text": "But instead the entire team"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 324160.0,
      "end_time": 326160.0,
      "text": "creates a shared mental model"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 326160.0,
      "end_time": 329160.0,
      "text": "that they can all agree on and move forward on."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 329160.0,
      "end_time": 331160.0,
      "text": "And this can be enhanced and augmented with"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 331160.0,
      "end_time": 334160.0,
      "text": "some emerging digital technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 334160.0,
      "end_time": 337160.0,
      "text": "And this is our great unveiling for today."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 337160.0,
      "end_time": 339160.0,
      "text": "And this is an emerging set of technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 339160.0,
      "end_time": 342160.0,
      "text": "that use large-screen displays"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 342160.0,
      "end_time": 345160.0,
      "text": "with intelligent calculation in the background"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 345160.0,
      "end_time": 347160.0,
      "text": "to make the invisible visible."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 347160.0,
      "end_time": 350160.0,
      "text": "Here what we can do is look at sustainability, quite literally."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 350160.0,
      "end_time": 353160.0,
      "text": "So a team can actually look at"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 353160.0,
      "end_time": 356160.0,
      "text": "all the key components that heat the structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 356160.0,
      "end_time": 358160.0,
      "text": "and make choices and then see the end result"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 358160.0,
      "end_time": 361160.0,
      "text": "that is visualized on this screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 361160.0,
      "end_time": 364160.0,
      "text": "So making images meaningful has three components."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 364160.0,
      "end_time": 367160.0,
      "text": "The first again, is making ideas clear by visualizing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 367160.0,
      "end_time": 369160.0,
      "text": "Secondly, making them interactive."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 369160.0,
      "end_time": 371160.0,
      "text": "And then thirdly, making them persistent."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 371160.0,
      "end_time": 373160.0,
      "text": "And I believe that these three principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 373160.0,
      "end_time": 377160.0,
      "text": "can be applied to solving some of the very tough problems"
    },
